<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='71258' id='t-71258'>We say in law enforcement things like,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='73093' id='t-73093'>&quot;Yeah, it's illegal to profile.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='76008' id='t-76008'>You know what?</span>
