<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='102049' id='t-102049'>I was just so tired.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='103904' id='t-103904'>I was tired of the vicious cycle,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='106081' id='t-106081'>and I was tired of it even
