<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123615' id='t-123615'>Y'all know what I'm talking about.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:16
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='125280' id='t-125280'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='126709' id='t-126709'>But we decided that I would retire.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='128456' id='t-128456'>But then there was a higher power than I.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='132492' id='t-132492'>There was a love for the city</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='135384' id='t-135384'>that I loved, that I grew up in,
