<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='142959' id='t-142959'>So we didn't retire.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144916' id='t-144916'>We didn't retire</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='146334' id='t-146334'>and so what happened was,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='148822' id='t-148822'>over the next -- I would say,
18 months, 19 months,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='153050' id='t-153050'>I had this passion to implement
