<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='164277' id='t-164277'>ready to retire as a drug sergeant --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='166865' id='t-166865'>and went from level to level to level,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='168723' id='t-168723'>until I find myself
as a district commander,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='171176' id='t-171176'>commander of the worst district
