</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='222772' id='t-222772'>But we still did it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='224190' id='t-224190'>We still did it because we listened
to that inner spirit,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226911' id='t-226911'>because I realized this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='228196' id='t-228196'>if I was to see real police reform</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='232269' id='t-232269'>in the communities that I had
authority over for public safety,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='236690' id='t-236690'>we had to change our stinkin' thinkin'.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='240728' id='t-240728'>We had to change it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='241905' id='t-241905'>And so what we did
is we started to think holistically</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244652' id='t-244652'>and not paramilitarily.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='246538' id='t-246538'>So we thought differently.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='248819' id='t-248819'>And we started to realize</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='250042' id='t-250042'>that it could never be
and never should have been</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='252376' id='t-252376'>us versus them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='254910' id='t-254910'>And so I decided to come
