<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='262952' id='t-262952'>and the eds, the meds,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='264262' id='t-264262'>and I would meet all the people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='265794' id='t-265794'>that made up the communities
that I had authority over.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='269205' id='t-269205'>So I met them and I began to listen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='271189' id='t-271189'>See, police have a problem.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='272665' id='t-272665'>Off the top, we want to bring
things into the community</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='275284' id='t-275284'>and come up with these extravagant
strategies and deployments,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='278276' id='t-278276'>but we never talk
to the community about them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280475' id='t-280475'>And we shove them into the community
and say, &quot;Take that.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='283806' id='t-283806'>But we said we'd get rid
of that stinkin' thinkin',</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='286227' id='t-286227'>so we talked to our communities.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='287799' id='t-287799'>We said, &quot;This is your community table.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='289691' id='t-289691'>We'll pull up a chair.
We want to hear from you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291978' id='t-291978'>What's going to work in your community?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293942' id='t-293942'>And then some great things
started to happen.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='296095' id='t-296095'>See, here's the thing:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='297270' id='t-297270'>I had to figure out a way to shift
130 cops that were under my tutelage</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='303014' id='t-303014'>from being occupiers of communities</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='305150' id='t-305150'>to being partners.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='307355' id='t-307355'>I had to figure out how to do that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='309071' id='t-309071'>Because here's the crazy thing:</span>
