<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='754384' id='t-754384'>This nation will become great again.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='756369' id='t-756369'>Because we have the same goal:
we all want peace.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='758812' id='t-758812'>We all want respect for one another.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='760570' id='t-760570'>We all want love.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='761744' id='t-761744'>And I believe we are back on that road,</span>
